String.Dest: Seemed like maybe you were starting to think you were too good for all this, or something... Too good for me, maybe.

String.Source: Yeah, sure. Of course. It can wait.
String.Dest: Yeah, sure. Of course. It can wait.

String.Source: We probably oughta get back to it.

String.Source: Well, I figure this is enough sharing or whatever, yeah?
String.Dest: Well, I figure this is enough sharing or whatever, yeah?

String.Source: Hell yeah it is. Two of us together, we're gonna blow a hole straight through the center of this shitty world.
String.Dest: Hell yeah it is. Two of us together, we're gonna blow a hole straight through the center of this shitty world.

String.Dest: But, come on... Seems like you've changed, and not for the better. Starting to wonder if you ain't got the stomach for this.

String.Dest: I was worried you were gettin' all high and mighty... Too good for me. Happy to say I was wrong.

String.Source: Can we do this later?

String.Dest: Look, I don't know how to talk about any of this shit... Feelings, I mean. This is all kinda new to me, okay?

String.Dest: I thought we really had something here... God, I can't believe I'm talking about all this shit... Look, it ain't working, okay?

String.Source: That means a lot, boss. Really does.

String.Source: Oh, yeah. Shit. Sorry, boss. Didn't mean nothin' by it.
String.Dest: Oh, yeah. Shit. Sorry, boss. Didn't mean nothin' by it.

String.Source: Right, okay. Wasn't meaning nothing by it, anyway. I'll, uhh, try and keep it in check, boss.
String.Dest: Right, okay. Wasn't meaning nothing by it, anyway. I'll, uhh, try and keep it in check, boss.

String.Dest: It's not weird, Gage. Far from it. I want more out of our relationship... Do you?

String.Dest: I probably shouldn't have said nothing, but... I ain't used to this, being all... "involved" and what not.

String.Source: Well... maybe it is getting a little weird after all. I'm not looking to screw up this situation, you know?

String.Dest: Ah, come on, boss. You wouldn't want nothin' to do with me, not with the fucked up life I've had.

String.Dest: Never thought I'd say this to a Raider, but... You're damn good company. I'm lucky to have you supporting me.

String.Source: This is getting way too touchy-feely for me, Gage. Let's dial it back - a lot.
String.Dest: This is getting way too touchy-feely for me, Gage. Let's dial it back - a lot.

String.Source: I appreciate the thought and all, but let's not let things get uncomfortable. Can we just stick to a working relationship here?
String.Dest: I appreciate the thought and all, but let's not let things get uncomfortable. Can we just stick to a working relationship here?

String.Source: I appreciate that, Gage.
String.Dest: I appreciate that, Gage.

String.Source: There's nothing weird about it, Gage. I've been thinking about it a lot too, and... I want us to be together.
String.Dest: Na tom není nic divného, Gagi. Bylo to dlouhé přemýšlení a... chci, abychom byli spolu.

String.Source: But really... thanks. I mean it
String.Dest: Ale vážně... díky. Myslím to vážně.

String.Source: Thanks, Gage. Means a lot to me.
String.Dest: Thanks, Gage. Means a lot to me.

String.Source: Of course. What's on your mind?
String.Dest: Samozřejmě. Co se děje?

String.Source: Is everything okay?
String.Dest: Je všechno v pořádku?

String.Source: I just... I needed to say I'm sorry.
String.Dest: I just... I needed to say I'm sorry.

String.Source: Thanks.
String.Dest: Díky.

String.Source: Yeah, boss. It is now.
String.Dest: Yeah, boss. It is now.

String.Source: Oh come on... we're supposed to be, I don't know... more than that, ain't we?
String.Dest: Oh come on... we're supposed to be, I don't know... more than that, ain't we?

String.Source: You are the Overboss, after all.
String.Dest: You are the Overboss, after all.

String.Source: Alright. Go ahead.
String.Dest: V pohodě. Povídej.

String.Source: It looked like things were going in a bad direction for us, so I said some shit that... Maybe I shouldn't have.

String.Source: That ain't something you see every day.
String.Dest: That ain't something you see every day.

String.Source: You're my kind of crazy, boss.
String.Dest: You're my kind of crazy, boss.

String.Source: So, you're not giving up on us?

String.Source: Forget it. I shouldn't have said anything.
String.Dest: Zapomeň na to. Neměl jsem ti nic říkat.

String.Source: This'll make a nice trophy!
String.Dest: This'll make a nice trophy!

String.Source: Ever wonder what it'd be like to have claws?... Me neither.
String.Dest: Ever wonder what it'd be like to have claws?... Me neither.

String.Source: Heh, yeah - ain't that the truth.
String.Dest: Heh, yeah - ain't that the truth.

String.Source: Yeah, yeah. Maybe so.
String.Dest: Yeah, yeah. Maybe so.

String.Source: But... I ain't never done anything like this. Ain't sure it'd work, you know?
String.Dest: But... I ain't never done anything like this. Ain't sure it'd work, you know?

String.Source: Anything you ever need, I'm here for you.
String.Dest: Anything you ever need, I'm here for you.

String.Dest: Anyone ever tell you your ass looks great in that Vault Suit?

String.Source: Are you sayin' what I think you're sayin'?
String.Dest: Are you sayin' what I think you're sayin'?

String.Source: Nah, I couldn't walk away just yet. Definitely not now that it seems like you got your head out of your ass.
String.Dest: Nah, I couldn't walk away just yet. Definitely not now that it seems like you got your head out of your ass.

String.Source: Really, Gage: haven't you ever thought about it? About us?
String.Dest: Really, Gage: haven't you ever thought about it? About us?

String.Source: I gotta tell ya, this wasn't really how I was thinking this little talk was gonna go.
String.Dest: I gotta tell ya, this wasn't really how I was thinking this little talk was gonna go.

String.Source: You are friggin' amazing, you know that?
String.Dest: You are friggin' amazing, you know that?

String.Source: Okay... We may have a problem here...
String.Dest: Okay... We may have a problem here...

String.Source: I'm glad things are okay between us.
String.Dest: I'm glad things are okay between us.

String.Source: Come on, you're talking to the Overboss here. Give me some credit.
String.Dest: Come on, you're talking to the Overboss here. Give me some credit.

String.Dest: I don't know what happens next. But, hell... Ain't nobody I'd rather have with me.

String.Dest: I mean, are you? No kidding around here, is this really what you want?

String.Dest: Tempting as it is to stay put, we best get movin'.

String.Dest: You a fan of antiques, boss?

String.Source: Okay, so can we avoid havin' this conversation again?

String.Source: 'specially not anybody that meant anything to me.

String.Dest: Okay, fine. I guess, maybe sometimes. We've been through a lot, and you're something else, all right.
